* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 18:04 Page   1
*                                      EXERC6.CBL
* Options: LIST(EXERC6.LST) ASMLIST(EXERC6.GRP)
     1 IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
     2
     3 PROGRAM-ID.    Exerc7.
     4 AUTHOR.        YHAGO PESSOA.
     5 INSTALLATION.  FATEC-SP.
     6 DATE-WRITTEN.  18/03/2025.
     7 DATE-COMPILED. 18-Mar-25 18:04.
     8 SECURITY.     APENAS O AUTOR PODE MODIFICA-LO.
     9
    10 ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
    11
    12   CONFIGURATION SECTION.
    13     SOURCE-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    14     OBJECT-COMPUTER.  MY-PC.
    15     SPECIAL-NAMES.    DECIMAL-POINT IS COMMA.
    16   INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
    17     FILE-CONTROL.
    18       SELECT   CAD-ENT   ASSIGN TO DISK
    19       ORGANIZATION IS  LINE  SEQUENTIAL.
    20       SELECT   CAD-SAI   ASSIGN TO DISK
    21       ORGANIZATION IS  LINE  SEQUENTIAL.
    22
    23 DATA DIVISION.
    24
    25   FILE SECTION.
    26     FD CAD-ENT
    27       LABEL   RECORD    STANDARD
    28       VALUE  OF FILE-ID IS "CAD-ENT.DAT".
    29     01 REG-ENT.
    30       02 MATRI-ENT     PIC 9(05).
    31       02 NOME-ENT      PIC X(30).
    32       02 SALARIO-ENT   PIC 9(05)V99.
    33     FD CAD-SAI
    34       LABEL   RECORD   STANDARD
    35       VALUE OF FILE-ID IS "CAD-SAI.DAT".
    36     01 REG-SAI.
    37       02 MATRI-SAI     PIC 9(05).
    38       02 NOME-SAI      PIC X(30).
    39       02 SALARIO-SAI   PIC 9(05)V99.
    40   WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
    41     77 FIM-ARQ  PIC X(03)  VALUE "NAO".
    42
    43 PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    44
    45   TESTE.
    46     PERFORM INICIO.
    47     PERFORM PRINCIPAL
    48       UNTIL FIM-ARQ EQUAL "SIM".
    49     PERFORM TERMINO
    50     STOP RUN.
    51
    52   INICIO.
    53     OPEN INPUT  CAD-ENT
    54          OUTPUT CAD-SAI.
    55     PERFORM LEITURA.
    56
    57   LEITURA.
* Microsoft COBOL Version 4.5        L2.4 revision 002 18-Mar-25 18:04 Page   2
*                                      EXERC6.CBL
    58     READ CAD-ENT
    59       AT END
    60       MOVE "SIM" TO FIM-ARQ.
    61
    62   PRINCIPAL.
    63     PERFORM GRAVACAO.
    64     PERFORM LEITURA.
    65
    66   GRAVACAO.
    67       MOVE MATRI-ENT   TO MATRI-SAI.
    68       MOVE NOME-ENT    TO NOME-SAI.
    69       MOVE SALARIO-ENT TO SALARIO-SAI.
    70       IF SALARIO-SAI > 3000
    71         WRITE REG-SAI
    72       END-IF.
    73
    74   TERMINO.
    75     CLOSE CAD-ENT
    76           CAD-SAI.
